Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock away your existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouting that you are here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new journey begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we survived through\Nthe changing seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we gained knowledge and strength,\N(just looks like a survival game)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the forgotten memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the feelings abandoned within\Nthe flows of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have also been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When sinking down,\Nwe learned loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we’ve met each other,\Nwe are no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unveil your feelings,\NThose high emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears will change your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pound your heartbeat\Nagainst the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re sure to meet,\NUnder the same flag of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take down Naruto\Nwith her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had I not applied the finishing blow\Nto her at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we would’ve been in danger instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know of no instance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Ninja Art: Kujaku\Nbeing defeated up until now…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Leaf Shinobi,\Nyour mission is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven’t taken back the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll search for it by ourselves.\NThank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshikage: The Buried Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy…\NI’m not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it…\NWhat happened after I fell off the cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be…?\NDid you save me, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\NI don’t really remember, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well anyway, you saved me! Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Naruto, a Ninja from\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I came to protect the star, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of stole it, lady…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Natsuhi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuhi? What?\NI’ve heard that name before…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That red star’s sure pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuhiboshi…\Nlt watches over me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the same name\Nas Natsuhiboshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru said it’s a star\Nthat protects him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Say, lady…\NDo you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru is my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So, you’re Sumaru’s mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Sumaru escaped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless thinking\Nthe muscle relaxants were still in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely the guys from\Nthe Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the ones who took him away…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’d be bad news if these circumstances\Nwere to be known
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Leaf, no,\Nby those in our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got to look high and low\Nfor Sumaru right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need to get rattled…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take care of them at\Nour leisure after we find the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. If we tell the Village Hidden\Nin the Leaves something like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they died during the mission…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could also convince Sumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned Natsuhi’s Chakra\Ninto my memory…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll reach the star
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we follow the remnants\Nof her Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto was…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Along with the Kunoichi\Nwho stole the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn’t see them\Nin the Valley of Death…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying they escaped from\Nthe valley
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the poison gas swirls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they might have crossed the border\Nand escaped safely to the forest…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let’s all look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the deal, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto helped all of you,\Ndidn’t he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don’t have an order\Nfrom Lord Akahoshi… Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have time to be waiting\Nfor an order! I’m going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go too, if it’s to look for Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizura, you can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be useful in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… I’ll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We safely rescued him from\Nthe Hoshikage’s medical room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where he was being held!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why was he in\NLord Hoshikage’s medical room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn’t a Ninja from\Nsome other village
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who knocked you all out\Nand took Sumaru away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi, the leader of your village\Nwas the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the Shinobi\Nwho made off with the star
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Shinobi who attacked all\Nof you were different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what Neji deduced\Nword for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Lord Akahoshi…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he do that to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean, Sumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems Lord Akahoshi\Nis hiding something from us…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it about time you guys realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi’s using you as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizura is not the exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys continue\Ntraining this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone will collapse and then…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be. That’s a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Akahoshi is not that\Nkind of person, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the Shinobi\Nwho stole the star will tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s find the Shinobi who disappeared,\Nwhatever the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forest in the Land of Bears\Nis deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only outsiders go,\Nthey’d just get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, work with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, the time will come\Nwhen we’ll need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Akahoshi…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to get a lead on\Nthe remnants of Natsuhi’s Chakra?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what’s called\Ngood old home-cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why’d you do something like\Nsteal the star, Sumaru’s mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the first and only time\NI took that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Training utilizing that star was painful\Nfor many Shinobi at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even caused many deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband Hotarubi and I\Nwho survived the training…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thought to seal the star to prevent\Nany more victims due to the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Tracking Unit immediately caught up\Nwith us after we had stolen the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Third Hoshikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotarubi…Natsuhi…\NYour thoughts are reasonable…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it happens, I was also wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the position of Hoshikage,\Nit was difficult to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to terminate\Nthe star training.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the hard-line faction\Nof the Star Village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might at some point\Nresume the training…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two must leave this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to keep an eye on\Nthe village from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it seems that the training\Nwill begin once again…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it with\Nyour power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Hoshikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Sumaru that…we died.\NPlease be good to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon allowing us to leave the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Lord Third Hoshikage completely\Nprohibited the star training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like us, the Third Hoshikage\Nwas also distressed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the damage from\Nthe star training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji was also talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are the effects from\Nthe star that severe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My husband Hotarubi died\Ndue to side effects
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a while after leaving the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might also die at any time\Nfrom the effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s go back to\Nthe village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Akahoshi directly to\Nstop the training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi is a man who puts\Nthe prosperity of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ahead of the lives of\Nthe children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of that,\Nhe has taken Sumaru hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has demanded that\NI return the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then the masked Ninja\Nfrom that time was…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Akahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sumaru’s mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve… 					Akahoshi has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the star being hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotarubi… Please protect\Nthe star, protect Sumaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The star is under that rock…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems the entrance\Nis sealed…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do with\Na boulder like this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to blow it up\Nlittle by little with Letter Bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t this brat die in\Nthe Valley of Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t be done in just like that,\Nbelieve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I just have to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Kujaku Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that move coming!\NBecome a sacrifice for my beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuhi… So you were alive too,\Nafter all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi, reconsider one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop the star training\Nand release the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have no more to do\Nwith the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hoshikage was stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and never wavered\Nin his opposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opposition to those of us\Nwho trained Star Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attempted to bring prosperity\Nto the village…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! As long as I,\Nthe Third Hoshikage, am alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the resumption of that training\Nwill never be allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your posts… That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who’s lost his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy and go to\Nthe other world…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our generation will\Nraise this village
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to rival that of\Nthe Five Great Hidden Villages…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this…really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was necessary for the sake\Nof the village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! We can do star training\Nas we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of all those\Nwho are training frantically,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believing in you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One’s even on the verge of dying!\NDo you understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice is unavoidable for\Nthe sake of village prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinobi is merely a tool for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of village prosperity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you’re doing is deceiving\Nthe people in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Star Village issue…\NI will settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotaka, Shisou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! He devoured\Nhis comrades’ Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Chakra beast has a full stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things won’t go as they did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk is cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sumaru’s mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday’s Call Sign,\Nwas all from my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a strange park,\NI play the Fuzz Guitar without enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yellow Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, counting to three,\NI open my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.10,0:22:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Moon I am still dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, look at my eyes,\Nas we face one another’s back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my eyes, when can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EveryDay EveryNight\NWith every word I can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, my messy feelings as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magical chord change, in a restless city
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A daily JAZZ Guitar played\Nin a soft minor key
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji, how’s Sumaru’s mom doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s stable for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but her condition can worsen\Nat any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Chakra Network that had\Nalready been weakened
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the side-effects of the star\Nbefore she received Akahoshi’s attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nher Chakra Network is all beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Granny Tsunade\Ncould heal her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if she were to use\Nthe Ninja Art: Kujaku any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no guarantee she’ll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:\N "Reunion: The Remaining Time"
